Flag tests
  Description:       Build the tests
  Default:           False
Flag postgres
  Description:       Use HDBC-postgresql (disable to remove postgresql dependency)
  Default:           True

Flag quasiquotes
  Description:       Compile quasi quote support (disable to remove template-haskell dependency)
  Default:           True


